1
00:01:27,616 --> 00:01:32,704
[Reblooming Blue]

2
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:36,032
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:40,128 --> 00:01:41,184
Ready.

4
00:01:41,879 --> 00:01:43,099
This way, This way.

5
00:01:43,099 --> 00:01:44,840
This way, come on.

6
00:01:45,504 --> 00:01:46,528
Good boy.

7
00:01:46,528 --> 00:01:47,648
Ready.

8
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:53,519
Over there. Run. Run.

9
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:55,400
Mudhead.

10
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,439
Where did you run off to again?

11
00:02:09,664 --> 00:02:10,688
Can we talk?

12
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,159
Are you here to talk to me about Jifeng?

13
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,120
Before I went to Shanghai,

14
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:31,280
you suddenly proposed to me

15
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,759
You must have foreseen this day coming.

16
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,879
I just want to tell you

17
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:41,840
that no matter what happens,

18
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,919
I will always be by your side.

19
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,712
I refuse.

20
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,304
It was you.

21
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:01,239
It was your encouragement

22
00:03:01,239 --> 00:03:03,159
that led me to what I wanted to do.

23
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,639
It was you

24
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:08,120
who made me believe I can do this well

25
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,680
and keep doing it.

26
00:03:10,464 --> 00:03:11,584
It was also you

27
00:03:12,384 --> 00:03:13,472
who made me feel

28
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,340
that I had so much,

29
00:03:16,340 --> 00:03:17,640
even love.

30
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,960
You made me feel like
the happiest person in the world.

31
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:27,744
What on earth

32
00:03:29,312 --> 00:03:30,360
do you want me

33
00:03:32,448 --> 00:03:33,504
to do

34
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:36,340
or to explain

35
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,959
for you to understand this

36
00:03:37,959 --> 00:03:39,620
has nothing to do with my love for you?

37
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:41,080
You've been using me from the very start.

38
00:03:44,352 --> 00:03:45,479
And you used me

39
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,879
to hurt the people I love and treasure most.

40
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:56,319
How can you still say you love me?

41
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,960
But I've loved you since Beijing.

42
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,759
And it's because I love you

43
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,360
that I have the courage to do everything.

44
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,400
You should understand me.

45
00:04:18,016 --> 00:04:19,040
I love you.

46
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,720
And we have a common destination.

47
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,879
That's your destination,

48
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:31,488
not mine.

49
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,720
What I want is simple.

50
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:45,440
I just didn't expect

51
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,199
what you want to be so complicated.

52
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,512
Let's break up.

53
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:04,896
Xiaoman.

54
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,919
How do you want me to explain

55
00:05:06,919 --> 00:05:09,360
to make you calm down and understand me?

56
00:05:10,432 --> 00:05:11,519
Will you please tell me?

57
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,839
Let's give each other

58
00:05:17,664 --> 00:05:18,784
some dignity.

59
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,920
I'm begging you.

60
00:05:56,704 --> 00:05:59,480
[Eight Months Ago, Beijing]

61
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,560
Before the next sorrow, people always

62
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,239
think the current pain

63
00:06:03,239 --> 00:06:04,319
is the worst.

64
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,000
On my last birthday,

65
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:09,880
I thought that my life back then

66
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,600
was absolutely the darkest moment.

67
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:14,399
And in every thrilling moment of my life,

68
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,000
there has been this man.

69
00:06:17,344 --> 00:06:21,472
[Yaosheng Investments Project Team One]

70
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,656
Hello?

71
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:50,079
I'm not done yet.

72
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:54,439
It's late. You should go ahead and eat.
Don't wait for me.

73
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,140
There's a lot of data here that's incomplete,

74
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:59,040
and I have to check the numbers one by one.

75
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:04,520
No way, they suddenly said
that it had to be submitted tomorrow,

76
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,639
so I must get it done today.

77
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:10,480
Alright, you guys eat for me, that's fine.

78
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:32,059
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

79
00:07:32,059 --> 00:07:34,759
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

80
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:38,680
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

81
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,820
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

82
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:44,900
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

83
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:47,580
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

84
00:07:47,580 --> 00:07:50,720
Chen Xiaoman isn't going to spend
her birthday working overtime, is she?

85
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:54,560
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

86
00:07:58,144 --> 00:07:59,200
Is she really not coming?

87
00:08:00,768 --> 00:08:01,824
You guessed it.

88
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,880
Make a wish quickly.

89
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:05,920
Make a wish.

90
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,639
What should we do?

91
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:11,279
Take the cake back,

92
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,560
and let's eat the hotpot.

93
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:53,320
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

94
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:56,660
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

95
00:08:56,660 --> 00:09:00,416
- ♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪
- Make a wish quickly.

96
00:09:00,416 --> 00:09:03,399
♪ Happy Birthday to you ♪

97
00:09:12,128 --> 00:09:13,219
Thank you.

98
00:09:13,219 --> 00:09:15,000
Why are you two up so late?

99
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,240
You've finally come back.

100
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,320
The process has to be completed.

101
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,399
What's important is to make a wish.

102
00:09:20,128 --> 00:09:21,216
[Happy Birthday to the Goddess Xiaoman]
It's so beautiful.

103
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,072
Come on, let's eat the cake.

104
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:27,648
I thought you were on a diet.

105
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:32,120
I'll eat mine tomorrow.

106
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,800
Okay, go to bed early.

107
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,320
- I can't hold on any longer.
- You should go to sleep quickly.

108
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:40,864
Are you all done?

109
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:44,200
Yes.

110
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,719
It was supposed to be submitted on Monday,

111
00:09:45,719 --> 00:09:48,120
but it turns out, it's needed
for the meeting tomorrow.

112
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:50,039
Otherwise, I wouldn't have stood you up.

113
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:52,360
Don't say that.

114
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,519
We can eat meals at any time.

115
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:57,159
And we can always
celebrate birthdays next year.

116
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:58,960
It's better to have a clear mind.

117
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:03,679
You're scrimping and saving every day
desperately making money.

118
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,879
How much money have you saved up by now?

119
00:10:09,216 --> 00:10:10,304
It's a secret.

120
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:14,300
Look at you.

121
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:15,960
You get so happy at the mere mention of money.

122
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:16,960
Come on.

123
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,420
The water heater is ready.

124
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:20,000
Would you like to take a hot shower first?

125
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,480
Okay, I'll go take a shower first.

126
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,256
[Bank Account Balance]

127
00:10:57,888 --> 00:10:58,976
Dad.

128
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:01,879
I'm about to accomplish a great goal.

129
00:11:02,879 --> 00:11:04,032
I'm awesome, aren't I?

130
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:16,559
Aunt, I might not be able
to come up with 500,000.

131
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,080
I understand all that.

132
00:11:21,088 --> 00:11:22,120
To tell the truth,

133
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:24,120
your uncle and I

134
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:26,879
never thought about taking your money.

135
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,000
As for you wanting to buy shares,

136
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:32,600
we feel that it's even more unnecessary.

137
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,920
Ultimately,

138
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:38,559
Jifeng is the Chen family's business.

139
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,639
Look at your cousins,

140
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,559
Tongtong, Yaoyao, they don't have any shares.

141
00:11:44,224 --> 00:11:45,279
Right?

142
00:11:45,279 --> 00:11:47,279
What's the hurry for you to buy shares?

143
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,720
Should a family really need
to keep such clear accounts?

144
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:54,080
It's my wish.

145
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:56,279
It's also something I want to do for Dad.

146
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,799
Anyway, it's already been said.

147
00:11:58,799 --> 00:12:00,399
I don't want to give up halfway.

148
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:07,720
As for the next phase,

149
00:12:08,879 --> 00:12:11,360
the company shares do need to be re-adjusted.

150
00:12:12,399 --> 00:12:13,559
But by that time,

151
00:12:14,759 --> 00:12:16,399
if you still haven't saved up enough money,

152
00:12:17,472 --> 00:12:18,560
as you know,

153
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:21,280
so many eyes are watching your uncle and me.

154
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,360
The two of us

155
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,440
can't make this decision anymore.

156
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,816
I know.

157
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,720
Ang'zai, am I not amazing?

158
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,639
I will spend two yuan
to give you a bath tomorrow.

159
00:12:44,679 --> 00:12:46,360
What do you think?

160
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:54,760
I really thought it would
be over before eight o'clock.

161
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,919
But when I opened the document,

162
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:58,799
many numbers were missing.

163
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,739
I was shocked.

164
00:13:00,739 --> 00:13:03,359
If they hadn't said they needed
it today, I really…

165
00:13:03,359 --> 00:13:05,719
I can't believe it, working until midnight.

166
00:13:05,719 --> 00:13:08,080
Haven't you seen on the Internet
how many young people these days

167
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:10,420
are dying from overwork?

168
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:11,979
You can't keep staying up late like this.

169
00:13:11,979 --> 00:13:13,440
I don't want to either.

170
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,479
I'm dead tired.

171
00:13:14,479 --> 00:13:15,960
If it wasn't for the fact that I receive…

172
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,260
some salary,

173
00:13:18,260 --> 00:13:19,360
I wouldn't be doing this.

174
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,159
You want money over life, right?

175
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:23,440
I want both.

176
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,419
How come you aren't dressed yet?

177
00:13:27,419 --> 00:13:29,460
I have administrative purchases today
that I can get reimbursed for.

178
00:13:29,460 --> 00:13:30,840
- Shall we take a taxi?
- Sure.

179
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,639
- Taking a taxi?
- Together? Shall we go?

180
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,279
You, you guys go ahead.

181
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,519
I need to go to the tax bureau.

182
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,392
- Bye.
- I'm leaving first.

183
00:13:39,392 --> 00:13:40,448
Be careful.

184
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,000
Stop eating, will you?

185
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,099
I'll be quick.

186
00:13:45,099 --> 00:13:46,360
I'll be ready as soon as I get dressed.

187
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:49,000
I'm telling you, we'll take a taxi.

188
00:13:49,799 --> 00:13:50,816
Right away.

189
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:55,700
They talked about layoffs last month.

190
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:57,160
I lose sleep every night.

191
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:59,200
I feel like I'll have to go home
soon, I'm telling you.

192
00:13:59,759 --> 00:14:01,720
Don't jinx yourself. It can't be you.

193
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:04,360
Hasn't your boss come back yet?

194
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,719
Not yet.

195
00:14:05,719 --> 00:14:07,200
He's always traveling.

196
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,928
I don't know what he's doing.

197
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,020
Think of a strategy.

198
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:13,279
Fight for what you should strive for.

199
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:15,080
It's not about that.

200
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:16,200
I think he looks down on me.

201
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,400
What are the odds?

202
00:14:19,039 --> 00:14:20,399
How did you end up with such a boss?

203
00:14:22,679 --> 00:14:23,776
I can only do my job well.

204
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:31,080
With so many people, the elevator
is going to be full again.

205
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,408
This way, this way.

206
00:14:34,816 --> 00:14:35,840
Here.

207
00:14:38,368 --> 00:14:39,392
Come on.

208
00:14:40,704 --> 00:14:41,780
Let's go.

209
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:42,944
Let's go.

210
00:14:42,944 --> 00:14:44,096
I'll go press the elevator button.

211
00:15:05,504 --> 00:15:09,440
[Fortune Plaza]

212
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,200
Pang Juan.

213
00:15:53,568 --> 00:15:54,688
It's done.

214
00:15:57,039 --> 00:15:58,399
Thank you.

215
00:15:58,399 --> 00:15:59,600
You're welcome.

216
00:16:00,399 --> 00:16:03,399
I… I want to ask you for a favor.

217
00:16:04,159 --> 00:16:05,519
What?

218
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:08,360
Didn't we agree on 5,000 before?

219
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,780
But I'm a bit tight on money now.

220
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:13,639
Would 3,000 be okay?

221
00:16:17,799 --> 00:16:19,759
You know this chart is not easy to make.

222
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,920
It almost took me a month.

223
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,480
And the information
you provided was not complete.

224
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:24,639
I had to calculate a lot of it myself.

225
00:16:24,639 --> 00:16:25,760
I know, I know.

226
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:27,519
This is not an easy job.

227
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:29,919
I'm not making excuses here,

228
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:32,559
but I truly have unspeakable difficulties.

229
00:16:33,159 --> 00:16:34,272
I…

230
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:37,320
I'm pregnant.

231
00:16:42,639 --> 00:16:44,639
It might be a personal physical issue,

232
00:16:45,279 --> 00:16:48,240
but I have severe morning sickness
and can't work well.

233
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,720
Otherwise, I wouldn't bother you, right?

234
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:54,440
Have you told the company?

235
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,860
Pang Juan, good morning.

236
00:16:55,860 --> 00:16:57,024
Morning.

237
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,472
How far along are you?

238
00:17:02,279 --> 00:17:03,296
Three months.

239
00:17:05,039 --> 00:17:06,680
Okay, 3,000 it is.

240
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:11,599
The rest can be considered
my gift money to you, okay?

241
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,500
You know, in our company,

242
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,200
there are several weddings this month.

243
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,480
I'm also a bit short on money.

244
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,712
Thank you.

245
00:17:21,319 --> 00:17:22,320
You're welcome.

246
00:17:22,320 --> 00:17:24,799
Alright, go back to work quickly,
and take care of your health.

247
00:17:26,272 --> 00:17:27,328
Go on, go on.

248
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,199
The head office's leaders
will arrive in half an hour.

249
00:17:56,199 --> 00:17:57,319
Half an hour?

250
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,440
Miss Tian, can you please help out?

251
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:03,260
It takes time to print materials.

252
00:18:03,260 --> 00:18:04,880
Come on, Administrative Dept.

253
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:06,880
I haven't had a sip of water
since I came to work today.

254
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:08,439
I have a pile of documents to deal with.

255
00:18:08,439 --> 00:18:10,960
If you say ten or eight minutes,
I can help you stall.

256
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,440
Half an hour is too long.

257
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:14,400
The more you talk with the group leaders,
the more mistakes you'll make.

258
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,519
It's difficult for.

259
00:18:17,279 --> 00:18:18,380
Dear Miss Tian.

260
00:18:18,380 --> 00:18:20,420
You always have so many issues.

261
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:22,059
Let me tell you, Ke Yan is finishing up

262
00:18:22,059 --> 00:18:23,600
his project negotiations.

263
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:25,160
Figure it out yourself, okay?

264
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:30,200
No wonder he doesn't reply to messages.

265
00:18:31,359 --> 00:18:33,960
Pang Juan, did you finish that form yesterday?

266
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:36,780
Miss Tian, I am working on it. There's still
some information to fill out.

267
00:18:36,780 --> 00:18:39,264
I have a meeting and I need it now.

268
00:18:39,264 --> 00:18:40,320
I'll organize it right away.

269
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:41,540
Is it this one? Let me take a look first.

270
00:18:41,540 --> 00:18:42,920
- No need.
- Let me see it.

271
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,472
Come with me.

272
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,920
Tell me, what's going on?

273
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,079
Miss Tian, I just haven't finished it.

274
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:04,680
I'm asking who did the annotations.

275
00:19:12,599 --> 00:19:14,240
You've been working for quite a few years now.

