286
00:20:01,799 --> 00:20:04,340
There is a data alignment
meeting of Fengyuan today.

287
00:20:04,340 --> 00:20:06,000
I asked Pang Juan

288
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,599
to prepare the required forms,

289
