but she asked Chen Xiaoman

290
00:20:09,500 --> 00:20:11,759
from Ke Yan's team to do it for her,

291
00:20:12,359 --> 00:20:13,640
violating the confidentiality agreement.

292
00:20:17,440 --> 00:20:19,759
Even though Ke Yan's projects
are mostly finished,

293
00:20:20,319 --> 00:20:22,799
