294
00:20:39,296 --> 00:20:40,384
Li.

295
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,160
For this year's Equestrian Week,

296
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,440
shall we have a little competition?

297
00:20:44,224 --> 00:20:45,344
Place a bet.

298
00:20:45,344 --> 00:20:48,160
Ke Yan, I really admire your energy.

299
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:51,319
You just got back from Yuyao
to accompany me in horse riding.

300
00:20:51,319 --> 00:20:53,039
