301
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:55,420
With your drive,

302
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:56,680
who wouldn't want

303
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:58,624
to trust you with the project?

304
00:21:00,319 --> 00:21:01,360
Once the time is ripe,

305
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:02,640
I'll arrange for you to meet with Fengyuan,

306
