308
00:21:08,799 --> 00:21:10,279
There's no way to preach him.

309
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:13,559
If you ask me,

310
00:21:13,559 --> 00:21:14,720
from the perspective of a vendor,

311
00:21:15,319 --> 00:21:16,699
I enjoy collaborating with someone

312
00:21:16,699 --> 00:21:18,780
experienced and capable like you the most.

313
00:21:18,780 --> 00:21:19,968
I couldn't ask for more.

314
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:21,640
You don't need to preach to me.

315
00:21:22,440 --> 00:21:24,480
You're confident like the buying party,

316
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,304
which I rarely see.

317
00:21:27,839 --> 00:21:29,460
I hope in this year's Equestrian Week,

318
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:31,279
