344
00:22:43,420 --> 00:22:45,640
Thank you for taking the time

345
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:47,839
to visit our company and provide guidance.

346
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,620
Today, we will have a

347
00:22:49,620 --> 00:22:52,279
data alignment meeting of Fengyuan Group.

348
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:56,280
Before the meeting, I would like
to report to the leaders

349
00:22:56,280 --> 00:22:58,439
the progress made

350
00:22:58,439 --> 00:23:00,020
on the Fengyuan Group's acquisition case.

351
00:23:00,020 --> 00:23:02,240
Our project team

352
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:05,420
