at the beginning of this year.

353
00:23:05,420 --> 00:23:07,220
And it is also one of the larger

354
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:09,480
projects for our company in recent years.

355
00:23:10,119 --> 00:23:13,640
Fengyuan Group is a strong player
in the cultural tourism industry.

356
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:14,679
Personally, I believe

357
00:23:14,679 --> 00:23:16,800
this acquisition case of Fengyuan Group

358
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:19,080
will create a significant impact

359
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:20,480
on the market.

360
00:23:39,079 --> 00:23:41,240
Recently, we have compiled some

361
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:44,840
consolidated cash flow statements
of Fengyuan Group

362
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:46,679
[Fengyuan 2022 Consolidated Cash Flow Statements]
and its seven subsidiaries.

363
00:23:46,679 --> 00:23:47,900
Let's take a look at them now.

364
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,480
Wu, scroll down.

365
00:23:57,600 --> 00:24:02,944
[Table Comments]

