386
00:25:26,359 --> 00:25:27,720
The condition of the blue
and white porcelain is good.

387
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:29,040
Yes, it's particularly good.

388
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:30,679
Ke Yan, see you at the Equestrian Week.

389
00:25:30,679 --> 00:25:31,880
Okay, see you then.

390
00:25:33,119 --> 00:25:34,200
Make sure it eats well.

391
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,200
Sure, no problem.

392
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:36,840
I must win the championship
at the Equestrian Festival this time.

393
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:37,888
Definitely.

394
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:39,808
Okay, see you later.

395
00:25:47,079 --> 00:25:48,599
Hey, what's the rush?

396
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,672
Got it.

397
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:13,599
Come on, what's the situation now?

398
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:16,680
The group leaders are here

399
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:17,720
and they require us

400
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:19,180
to provide a solution today.

401
00:26:19,180 --> 00:26:20,839
That's why we urgently called you back.

402
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:23,240
I think

403
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:24,780
Tian Xiwen must be up to something.

404
00:26:24,780 --> 00:26:26,280
With Tian Xiwen's intelligence,

405
00:26:26,280 --> 00:26:27,680
