408
00:26:32,839 --> 00:26:34,760
The HR department has already
notified all departments

409
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:36,039
to finish work one hour late.

410
00:26:57,680 --> 00:26:59,319
Isn't this our great contributor?

411
00:27:01,279 --> 00:27:03,799
I heard you signed the contract
right there in Jiangxi.

412
00:27:04,519 --> 00:27:05,599
That's pretty efficient.

413
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:07,720
You look travel-weary.

414
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:10,400
Why aren't you home to rest?

415
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,520
Are you behind this?

416
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,344
Behind what?

417
00:27:14,559 --> 00:27:15,920
Don't falsely accuse me.

418
00:27:27,296 --> 00:27:28,400
What's that?

419
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:29,519
Precious Chinese medicine.

420
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:32,920
Overthinking can easily lead to anxiety.

421
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,319
Take good care of your health.

422
00:27:45,319 --> 00:27:46,368
What's going on?

423
00:27:58,519 --> 00:27:59,820
You have too much spare time,

424
00:27:59,820 --> 00:28:01,780
enough to work on projects for another group.

425
00:28:01,780 --> 00:28:03,279
It didn't affect my work

426
00:28:03,839 --> 00:28:05,300
or the company.

427
00:28:05,300 --> 00:28:07,008
Why don't you do the cleaning work then?

428
00:28:07,008 --> 00:28:08,159
It doesn't make money.

429
00:28:08,159 --> 00:28:09,440
Quite honest, aren't we?

430
00:28:11,319 --> 00:28:12,759
I didn't recognize you as a money grubber.

431
00:28:18,272 --> 00:28:19,392
Boss.

432
00:28:21,079 --> 00:28:23,720
Look, I've been on your team
for quite a few years now.

433
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:26,048
Just help me out.

434
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:29,659
I promise that I won't dare to do it again.

435
00:28:29,659 --> 00:28:32,240
- There won't be a next time.
- The project we worked on for half a year

436
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,880
was almost within our grasp.

437
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:36,839
Just because of this mess you made,

438
00:28:37,599 --> 00:28:39,240
I have to come back
and report to the company now.

439
00:28:43,319 --> 00:28:44,320
I have a premonition.

440
00:28:45,599 --> 00:28:47,640
Chances are I've made
a wedding dress for someone else.

441
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:50,359
If I help you, who'll help me?

442
00:28:51,559 --> 00:28:53,000
It's you or me.

443
00:28:53,559 --> 00:28:54,599
What an easy choice.

444
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:34,944
Xiaoman.

445
00:29:36,119 --> 00:29:37,700
I didn't expect things

446
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:39,319
to develop to this extent.

447
00:29:43,799 --> 00:29:45,319
It was consensual, after all.

448
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:48,599
No one should be sorry.

449
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:53,640
Being discovered just means we're unlucky.

450
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:01,376
Which project?

451
00:30:02,688 --> 00:30:03,839
The Fengyuan one.

452
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:07,459
That's your team's project.

453
00:30:07,459 --> 00:30:09,299
And the data is all confidential.

454
00:30:09,299 --> 00:30:10,599
It's not appropriate for me to take over.

455
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,392
Did you just finish a meeting?

456
00:30:32,832 --> 00:30:33,920
What's wrong?

457
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:35,039
Are you busy lately?

458
00:30:35,599 --> 00:30:36,799
Can you help me out a bit?

459
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:39,559
I have a consolidated cash flow statement task.
Could you help me with it?

460
00:30:40,839 --> 00:30:41,920
Which project?

461
00:30:43,319 --> 00:30:44,384
The Fengyuan one.

462
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,780
That's your team's project.

463
00:30:47,780 --> 00:30:49,640
And the data is all confidential.

464
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,720
It's not appropriate for me to take over.

465
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:53,880
If you don't tell and I don't tell,
who would find out?

466
00:30:55,119 --> 00:30:56,640
It's not a matter of telling or not telling.

467
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:57,880
It's against the rules.

468
00:30:57,880 --> 00:31:00,480
5,000. I won't let you work for nothing.

469
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:02,860
It's not about the money.

470
00:31:02,860 --> 00:31:04,599
I know that.

471
00:31:06,519 --> 00:31:07,580
I owe you a big favor.

472
00:31:07,580 --> 00:31:08,839
Can you do me this favor?

473
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,759
No, I can't.

474
00:31:10,759 --> 00:31:11,760
Please, just help me out.

475
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:14,520
You know, if it wasn't
for an absolute necessity,

476
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:16,240
I wouldn't ask you for help.

477
00:31:17,079 --> 00:31:18,079
Please, just help me out.

478
00:31:18,079 --> 00:31:19,640
I'll owe you a big one.

479
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:22,480
I'll take that as a yes.
I still have a meeting to attend.

480
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:24,000
I'll send you the materials right away.

481
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:25,152
I'm off.

