505
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,480
and resign on your own initiative.

506
00:32:57,960 --> 00:32:59,079
But we gave it some thought afterward.

507
00:32:59,839 --> 00:33:01,100
Considering your performance

508
00:33:01,100 --> 00:33:03,200
