for the next two quarters.

512
00:33:12,128 --> 00:33:13,152
Do you accept that?

513
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:15,808
I do.

514
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:19,240
After the group's discussion,

515
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:21,720
regarding your employee Chen Xiaoman,

516
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,799
