517
00:33:33,359 --> 00:33:34,432
I don't agree.

518
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:42,720
If Pang Juan asked you for help,

519
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:45,319
and you were just cooperating
to assist a colleague,

520
00:33:45,880 --> 00:33:47,079
then this matter

521
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,832
wouldn't be a big deal.

522
00:33:49,759 --> 00:33:51,460
But you charged a fee,

523
00:33:51,460 --> 00:33:53,880
and it involved the company's secrets,

524
00:33:54,599 --> 00:33:57,200
the nature of this issue
is completely different.

525
00:34:00,599 --> 00:34:01,680
Do you have any explanation?

526
00:34:08,159 --> 00:34:09,199
Then do you accept

527
00:34:10,039 --> 00:34:11,320
our decision?

528
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,480
I do.

529
00:34:23,519 --> 00:34:26,339
Since Chen Xiaoman has accepted
this outcome herself,

530
00:34:26,339 --> 00:34:28,879
I suggest that you should not go against

531
00:34:28,879 --> 00:34:30,100
the company's decision.

532
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,296
Mr. Ke,

533
00:34:37,079 --> 00:34:38,920
