534
00:34:42,048 --> 00:34:43,080
Mr. Ke,

535
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:46,340
in light of the adverse impact
caused by the Chen Xiaoman incident,

536
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:47,500
the group advises you

537
00:34:47,500 --> 00:34:48,940
to promptly conduct

538
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,719
